abel category-label-boerum-hill">Boerum Hill:</span> <a class="title blotter" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20221121162823/https://www.brooklynpaper.com/84th-precinct-stabbing-on-schermerhorn-street/">84th Precinct: Stabbing on <span class="lgwd">Schermerhorn</span> Street</a></span></li><li class="listing-item article-container cards-design"><i class="fa fa-shield" aria-hidden="true"></i><span class="title-wrapper"><span class="category-display category-label category-label-brighton-beach">Brighton Beach:</span> <a class="title blotter" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20221121162823/https://www.brooklynpaper.com/60th-precinct-woman-steals-ashes-from-chapel/">60th Precinct: Woman steals ashes from chapel</a></span></li></ul>
